The paper discusses the design and implementation of an array data type for relational database systems to support scientific applications, specifically in the fields of astrophysics and fluid dynamics simulations. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the database (cs.DB), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and software engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories.
